2.1.6. objectlistiterator¶

2.1.6.1. Module d1_client.objectlistiterator¶

Implements an iterator that iterates over the entire ObjectList for a DataONE node. Data is retrieved from the target only when required.

Created:

2010-04-07
Author:

DataONE (Vieglais)
Dependencies:
  • python 2.6

Example:

$python objectlistiterator.py -b "http://knb-mn.ecoinformatics.org/knb/d1"     -m 5 -s 1000
